quran[21]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,49,"Àti pé gbogbo n̄ǹkan ni A ṣẹ̀dá rẹ̀ ní oríṣi méjì-méjì nítorí kí ẹ lè lo ìrántí.{1}.",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Yāsīn; 36:36.
  51,50,"Nítorí náà, ẹ sá lọ sí ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu (nípa ìronúpìwàdà). Dájúdájú èmi ni olùkìlọ̀ pọ́nńbélé fún yín láti ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀."
  51,51,"Ẹ má ṣe mú ọlọ́hun mìíràn mọ́ Allāhu. Dájúdájú èmi ni olùkìlọ̀ pọ́nńbélé fún yín láti ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀."
  52,40,"Tàbí ò ń bèèrè owó-ọ̀yà kan lọ́wọ́ wọn, ni gbèsè fi wọ̀ wọ́n lọ́rùn?"
  52,41,"Tàbí ìmọ̀ ìkọ̀kọ̀ wà lọ́dọ̀ wọn, tí wọ́n sì ń kọ ọ́ sílẹ̀?"
  52,42,"Tàbí wọ́n ń gbèrò ète kan ni? Nígbà náà, àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́, àwọn l’ó máa f’orí kó ète náà."
  53,34,"tí ó fi díẹ̀ tọrẹ, tí ó sì di ìyókù mọ́wọ́!"
  53,35,"Ṣé ìmọ̀ ìkọ̀kọ̀ wà ní ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ, tí ó sì ń rí i (pé ẹlòmíìràn l’ó ma bá òun jìyà lọ́run)?"
  53,36,"Tàbí wọn kò fún un ní ìró ohun tó wà nínú tírà (Ànábì) Mūsā ni,"
  54,25,"Ṣé òun ni wọ́n sọ tírà ìrántí kalẹ̀ fún láààrin wa? Rárá o, òpùrọ́ onígbèéraga ni.”"
  54,26,"Ní ọ̀la ni wọn yóò mọ ta ni òpùrọ́ onígbèéraga."
  54,27,"Dájúdájú Àwa máa rán abo ràkúnmí sí wọn; (ó máa jẹ́) àdánwò fún wọn. Nítorí náà, máa wò wọ́n níran ná, kí o sì ṣe sùúrù.{1}.",footnotes:1:Ṣe sùúrù láì níí fi ẹjọ́ wọn sùn mọ́.
  55,19,"(Allāhu) mú odò méjì (odò oníyọ̀ àti odò aládùn) ṣàn pàdé ara wọn."
  55,20,"Gàgá kan sì wà láààrin àwọn méjèèjì tí wọn kò sì lè tayọ ẹnu-ààlà (rẹ̀ láààrin ara wọn)."
  55,21,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?"
  56,10,"Àwọn aṣíwájú sì ni àwọn aṣíwájú."
  56,11,"Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni alásùn-únmọ́ (Allāhu)"
  56,12,"nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra."
  57,1,"Ohunkóhun tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ ń ṣàfọ̀mọ́ fún Allāhu. Òun sì ni Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n."
  57,2,"TiRẹ̀ ni ìjọba àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀. Ó ń sọ ẹ̀dá di alààyè. Ó sì ń sọ ẹ̀dá di òkú. Òun ni Alágbára lórí gbogbo n̄ǹkan."
  57,3,"Òun ni Àkọ́kọ́ àti Ìkẹ́yìn. Ó hàn (pẹ̀lú àmì bíbẹ Rẹ̀). Ó sì pamọ́ (fún gbogbo ojú nílé ayé). Òun ni Onímọ̀ nípa gbogbo n̄ǹkan."